=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
זכריהוּ  -  זכריה / zekaryâh  zekaryâhû / zek-ar-yaw', zek-ar-yaw'-hoo
=== Etymology ===

From [[זכר]] {{HH|2142}} and [[יהּ]] {{HH|3050}}; Jah has remembered; 
=== Proper noun ===
Zecarjah, the name of twenty nine Israelites: - Zachariah, Zechariah.